1. setup everything as written in README. assuming the gateways are still intact and you dont have to put in the port forwarding rules again
2. first run the vpn normally using the -v verbose flag. verify that you can ssh fron virtualhosta1 to virtualhostb1
3. now re run the vpn with -v -t 1 flags (testnum==1 for changing hash and dropping packets)
	now, the host at which this was set the packets should be dropped and communication should not happen. verify by showing verbose printouts!

4. can also show forged certificates test
